    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i guess. but \"making a day bearable\" feels like such a pathetic excuse for staying. it’s like being told to enjoy the view while the house is burning down. if you know the end is coming and you can't stop it, isn't it just more dignified to just... not be part of it? to not have to witness the slow decline? it feels more honest to just check out than to pretend everything is fine.",
